Baaj Adebule (amụrụ na 25 Ọktoba 1988) bụ onye na-eme ihe nkiri, onye nlereanya, na onye na-eme ihe nkiri si Ogun Steeti na Southwestern Nigeria

Ọ pụtara na ihe nkiri Nollywood kemgbe afọ 2012. Ọ malitere ọrụ ya na M-Net's soap opera Tinsel ma pụta na ihe nkiri na usoro TV dịka Hush, The Men's Club, Payday, Zena, Uncloaked, The Governor, The Missing, A Soldier's Story 1 & 2, Omo Wa, Beast Within, na The Moles
A mụrụ Adebule na Jalupon Hospital na Surulere, Lagos
Ọ nọrọ ọtụtụ oge nwata ya na Maryland Lagos, ebe ọ gara ụlọ akwụkwọ praịmarị Seat of Wisdom na ụlọ akwụkwọ sekọndrị Caleb
Ọ kwagara Surulere mgbe nne na nna ya gbara alụkwaghịm n'afọ 2005
Adebule bụ onye Yoruba ma bụrụ onye obodo Ijebu Ode nke Ogun Steeti
A zụlitere ya n'ụlọ Ndị Kraịst
Nna ya bụ onye injinia na nne ya bụ onye na-ahụ maka ego na onye ọchụnta ego
Ọ bụ nwa nke ikpeazụ n'ime ụmụ itoolu sitere n'ọtụtụ alụmdi na nwunye.
Afọ ụlọ akwụkwọ ya lekwasịrị anya na agụmakwụkwọ, ebe nne na nna ya kwusiri ike mkpa agụmakwụkwọ
Mgbe ọ dị obere, ọ lekwasịrị anya na egwuregwu na nka, na-egwu bọọlụ, basketball, badminton, table tennis, na track.
Na akụkọ ndụ ya, Adebule kwuru na ọ bụ onye otu ukwe ụka obodo site na nwata yana onye otu klọb nka nke ụlọ akwụkwọ ya
A maara Adebule karịsịa maka ịhụnanya ya maka ihe nkiri, nke ọ lekwasịrị anya na ya mgbe nne na nna ya gbara alụkwaghịm.
N'afọ 2005, Adebule malitere ịga Mahadum Covenant dị na Ogun Steeti iji mụọ akụ na ụba
Ọ gụsịrị akwụkwọ na klas nke abụọ na 2009
Mgbe ọ gụsịrị akwụkwọ, ọ malitere itinye aka na nka na egwuregwu
Ọ rụrụ ọrụ na MultiChoice ihe fọrọ nke nta ka ọ bụrụ afọ abụọ tupu ọ kwụsị iji lekwasị anya na ntụrụndụ.
Adebule malitere ọrụ ime ihe nkiri na ịme ihe ngosi n'afọ 2010 mgbe ọ na-arụ ọrụ itoolu ruo ise
Ọ ga-aga maka nyocha na foto n'oge ezumike ya
O mechara nweta obere oge na telenovela Tinsel.
Site na nkwado nke ndị enyi ya na ndị ezinụlọ ya, ọ bụ onye asọmpi na 2011 Mr
Nigeria pageant, ebe ọ bịara nke anọ
N'afọ 2012, ọ malitere ime ihe nkiri na ịme ihe ngosi oge niile.
Adebule pụtara na Hush, na-egosi Adze
Ọ pụtara na ihe nkiri dị ka 5ive, The Governor, Uncloaked, The Missing, Payday, na Battleground Showdown
A tọhapụghị ya
